X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Event Type";ID=21;TYPE=number:Job-Search Stra
 tegies
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Contact Name";ID=28322;TYPE=SingleLine:Non Ko
 ntak:  Maryse Brock:
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Contact Email";ID=28324;TYPE=Email:<a href="m
