DESCRIPTION:Room: North Seattle WorkSource Computer Lab<br>Workshop Lang
 uage Option: English<br>Additional Information: Please go to <a href="ht
 tp://www.worksourcewa.com" target="_blank">WorkSourceWA.com</a> and crea
 te your account prior to attending this workshop.\n\nBecause this worksh
 op is being held in our computer lab\, you can absolutely work on your r
 esume while we move through the workshop!<br>Approved Unemployment Insur
 ance (UI) Job Search Activity: Yes<br><br>Craft Your Story. Customize Yo
 ur Success. &#160\;<br>Your r&#233\;sum&#233\; doesn&#8217\;t need to be
  complicated to be effective&#8212\;it just needs to tell the right stor
 y. In this workshop\, you&#8217\;ll learn how to build a clear\, profess
 ional r&#233\;sum&#233\; from the ground up and make simple\, strategic 
 customizations that help you stand out to employers.<br><br>Whether you&
 #8217\;re creating your first r&#233\;sum&#233\; or refreshing an old on
 e\, this workshop will give you practical tools you can use immediately.
  We&#8217\;ll walk through what hiring managers look for\, how to highli
 ght your strengths\, and how small tweaks can make a big impact. You&#82
 17\;ll leave with a better understanding of your own experience\, and th
 e confidence to tailor your r&#233\;sum&#233\; for any opportunity.<br><
 br>If you&#8217\;re ready to take the next step in your career with a r&
 #233\;sum&#233\; that truly represents you\, this workshop is the perfec
 t place to start. Reserve your spot and start shaping your success.<br><
 br>&#160\;
