DESCRIPTION:Room: 142<br>Contact Name: Jerrell Briscoe<br>Contact Email:
  jerrell.briscoe@esd.wa.gov<br>Workshop Language Option: English<br>Addi
 tional Information: Please go to <a href="http://www.worksourcewa.com" t
 arget="_blank">WorkSourceWA.com</a> and create your account prior to att
 ending this workshop.<br>Event Registration: Sign Up Required<br>Approve
 d Unemployment Insurance (UI) Job Search Activity: Yes<br><br><p>The Vet
 eran Job Club is a supportive\, collaborative space designed to help Vet
 erans build confidence and momentum in their job search.<br>Participants
  connect with fellow Veterans\, share strategies\, explore employment re
 sources tailored to the Veteran community\, and learn practical tools fo
 r navigating today&#8217\;s job market.<br>Together\, we problem&#8209\;
 solve challenges\, strengthen networking skills\, and create a community
  where Veterans can ask questions\, exchange insights\, and support one 
 another on the path to meaningful employment.</p>
