DESCRIPTION:Contact Name: Christine Simpson and Matt Pangallo<br>Contact
  Phone: matthew.pangallo@esd.wa.gov<br>Contact Email: christine.simpson@
 esd.wa.gov<br>Workshop Language Option: English<br>Additional Informatio
 n: Please go to <a href="http://www.worksourcewa.com" target="_blank">Wo
 rkSourceWA.com</a> and create your account prior to attending this works
 hop.\n&nbsp\;<p>Video conferencing will use a large portion of bandwidth
  and data. Before signing up\, be sure you have a data plan or reliable 
 Wi-Fi access that can accommodate this. To attend the workshop\, you are
  encouraged to use a device capable of viewing video and content and hav
 e audio capability.</p><p>\nA waitlist option will be enabled for this e
 vent. This waitlist is automated and if an attendee drops their registra
 tion\, the next registrant on the waitlist will be invited. Each worksho
 p requires a separate registration.</p><p>\nWhen you sign up for this ev
 ent\, please use the same name and email address that you use with your 
 worksourcewa.com account\, if possible.\n\nContact the facilitator liste
 d above in the contact lines for any additional questions or changes.\n
 \n&nbsp\;</p><p><em>If you need an accommodation to participate in this t
 raining\, please contact the facilitators for this workshop. Please prov
 ide your name\, accommodation request\, and your town/city of residence.
  Please make your accommodation request as early as possible so arrangem
 ents can be made.</em></p><br>Event Registration: Sign Up Required<br>Ap
 proved Unemployment Insurance (UI) Job Search Activity: Yes<br><br><p><s
 trong>The Self</strong><strong>&#8208\;</strong><strong>Employment Assis
 tance Program (SEAP) may be a great opportunity if you want to start a b
 usiness!</strong></p><p>&#160\;</p><p>Once approved\, SEAP is a unique p
 rogram that enables you to:</p><ul> <li>Receive entrepreneurial counseli
 ng and business coaching through a pre&#8208\;approved training provider
 	</li><li>Continue to collect Unemployment Insurance (UI) benefits while
  developing your business plans	</li><li>Work on creating your business 
 and waives the weekly work&#8208\;search requirement</li></ul><p>&#160\;
 </p><p><strong>You are invited to attend a virtual workshop to explore:<
 /strong></p><ul> <li>SEAP Program Details	</li><li>Eligibility Requireme
 nts and Deadlines	</li><li>Approved Training Provider Lists	</li><li>App
 lication Process	</li><li>Your Responsibilities	</li><li>Other important
  information</li></ul><p>&#160\;</p><p>&#160\;</p>&#160\;
