 Registration: Sign Up Required<br>Approved Unemployment Insurance (UI) J
 ob Search Activity: Yes<br><br><p>Are you receiving Unemployment Insuran
 ce benefits and considering enrolling in some additional training to enh
 ance your skills or to change your Career Path? If so\, you will need to
